rows.label: tlk43400443_03_msg0002
rows.name:
You know there are all these refugees
from Acedia now, right?

rows.label: tlk43400443_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, thanks to them, our rations
have gotten smaller than ever.

rows.label: tlk43400443_03_msg0004
rows.name:
How am I supposed to feed my
children on this?

rows.label: tlk43400443_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I mean, I know they're victims too...
But if we keep on like this, everyone's
going to suffer - us and them!

rows.label: tlk43400443_03_msg0006
rows.name:
The bigwigs need to stop thinking
about their own interests and start
putting the country first...
